158
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,590
Just be here quietly.

159
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:31,800
We'll be home soon.

160
00:10:47,350 --> 00:10:48,440
Huo. Where are you?

161
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:50,040
