178
00:13:15,470 --> 00:13:16,230
Go home.

179
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:17,990
Drive safe.

180
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,230
Why are you here?

181
00:13:51,990 --> 00:13:53,830
